&quot;/g I have lost Brell's blessing!  Worthy cleric, can you perform the rites of Heroism and Shield of Words?&quot;<br>
&quot;/g Enchantress, can your magic grant my blades the speed of the wind?&quot;<br>
&quot;/g Friend Druid, my feet move slowly.  Can you give me the speed of a wolf?&quot;<br>
<br>
etc.<br>
<br>
No, after a bit you will type &quot;Hero, SHoW, speed, and SOW down.&quot;  Otherwise yer fingers are gonna hurt.<br>
